                    <p class="lead">
                        The Minerals Council South Africa launched the first National Day of Women in Mining highlighting its focus on the implementation of initiatives designed to achieve stretch targets for the representation and
                        advancement of women in the South African mining industry.
                    </p>
                    <a class="btn btn-default" href="/industry-news/media-releases/2020/send/60-2020/1215-minerals-council-south-africa-launches-first-national-day-of-women-in-mining" rel="external">Media Release</a>
                    <a class="btn btn-default" href="/downloads/send/19-latest/1214-women-in-mining-strategy" rel="external">Presentation</a>
                    <a class="btn btn-default" type="button" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#wimvideo" rel="external">Video</a>
                    <a class="btn btn-default" href="/special-features/1139-national-day-of-women-in-mining-2020" rel="external">Read more</a>
